PB  - INFORMS
N2  - This is an informative paper about the position and situation of R & D (applied) in Eastern and Western Europe. Based on different sources the study also shows a part of the growing differences (different opinions) about importance, understanding and methods to evaluate the efficiency of R & D. It also discusses the ?double concept? of R & D efficiency, namely as a summary of successful research results and product application with marketing effect.
