TY  - JOUR
T1  - A Branch-and-Bound Algorithm for Multi-Level Fixed-Charge Problems
AU  - Jones, Arnold P.
AU  - Soland, Richard M.
Y1  - 1969/09/01
PY  - 1969
DA  - 1969/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.16.1.67
